Name: A Smuggler's Reward
Description: "Don't keep me waiting!" Isery pouts prettily, and rustles their silks. "Do you have a little present for me?"

DefaultEvent.Description:
Isery snatches the notes from your hands, and starts flicking through the pages. "I'll have a reward sent to your ship." They look up and smile at you vaguely, eyes glazed as a honey-seeker's. "Oh, my dear, what a treasure you are."

 You summon an answering smile, and slip away the moment they are distracted.

ChildBranches.Name: A well-earned reward
ChildBranches.Description: You hand over the Alarming Scholar's notes.
